node.text:
#TransformationTuesday - LEFT or RIGHT❓In Jewish tradition, there’s a belief about Tuesdays that goes all the way back to the beginning.

When God created the world, He said “it is good” on every single day of the week—except Tuesday, on Tuesday God said “it is good”…twice! That’s why many Jews believe Tuesday is doubly blessed by God.
•
Indeed I do feel blessed to have both of those sides in me … I feel like they complete each other 😇
